covidRaceDataCombined.apiNote: A combined Asian and Pacific Islander category is reported, which we treat as Asian and NHPI combined in our calculations per 100K. We report this category under the "Asian" category in our totals.
covidRaceDataCombined.latinxNote: Our calculations assume Hispanic or Latino ethnicity may include any race.
covidRaceDataCombined.mutExclNote: Race categories are mutually exclusive and defined as Not Hispanic or Latino.
covidRaceDataCombined.name: New York
covidRaceDataCombined.otherNote: One or more standard race categories are not reported or otherwise specified by the state. These categories may or may not be included in the "Other race" category in our data.
covidRaceDataCombined.popTableNote: Population sizes are taken from the Census Bureau’s 2019 ACS 5-Year estimates Table B03002.
